ll Tuttle (swimmer)|Bill Tuttle]].<ref name=\"1904OG SR\"/> Head coach: [[Alex Meffert]].<ref name=\"Olympians\"/>\n*: [[Missouri Athletic Club]]: [[Gwynne Evans]], [[Augustus Goessling|Gus Goessling]], [[John Meyers (swimmer)|John Meyers]], [[William R. Orthwein|Bill Orthwein]], [[Amedee Reyburn]], [[Frank Schreiner]], [[Manfred Toeppen]].<ref name=\"1904OG SR\"/>\n\n* {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Water polo at the 1920 Summer Olympics|1920 Antwerp]] \u2013 4th place\n*: [[Clement Browne]], [[James Carson (water polo)|James Carson]], [[Harry Hebner]] <small>(C)</small>, [[Sophus Jensen]], [[Mike McDermott (athlete)|Mike McDermott]], [[Perry McGillivray]], [[Norman Ross]], [[Preston Steiger]], [[Herbert Taylor (swimmer)|Herbert Taylor]], [[Herb Vollmer]], [[William Vosburgh]].<ref name=\"1920OG\"/><ref name=\"1920OG PDF\"/><ref name=\"1920OG SR\"/> Head coach: [[Otto Wahle]].<ref name=\"Otto Wahle\"/><ref name=\"Otto Wahle2\"/>\n\n* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Water polo at the 1924 Summer Olympics|1924 Paris]] \u2013 '''{{Bronze3}} Bronze medal'''\n*: [[Arthur Austin (water polo)|Art Austin]], [[Charles E. Collett|Elmer Collett]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Jam Handy]], [[Oliver Horn]], [[Fred Lauer]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[George Mitchell (water polo)|George Mitchell]], [[John Norton (water polo)|John Norton]], [[Wally O'Connor]], [[George Schroth]], [[Herb Vollmer]] <small>(C)</small>, [[Johnny Weissmuller]].<ref name=\"1924OG\"/><ref name=\"1924OG PDF\"/><ref name=\"1924OG SR\"/> Head coach: [[Harry Hebner]] (did not go){{efn |name=Harry_Hebner}}<ref name=\"Harry Hebner2\"/> / [[Otto Wahle]]<ref name=\"Otto Wahle\"/><ref name=\"Otto Wahle2\"/>.\n\n* {{flagicon|NED}} [[Water polo at the 1928 Summer Olympics|1928 Amsterdam]] \u2013 7th place\n*: [[John Cattus]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Harry Daniels (water polo)|Harry Daniels]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Joseph Farley (water polo)|Joseph Farley]], [[Richard Greenberg (water polo)|Richard Greenberg]], [[Sam Greller]], [[George Mitchell (water p